  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Evoglitin in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes and Non-alcoholic Fatty Liver Diseases</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Double-blind, Active-controlled, Randomized, Parallel, Phase IV Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Evogliptin in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes and Non-alcoholic Fatty Liver Diseases</official_title>
