  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A multicenter, double-blind, active-controlled, randomized, parallel, phase IV clinical trial
      to evaluate the efficacy and safety of evogliptin in patients with type 2 diabetes and
      non-alcoholic fatty liver diseases
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      1. Evogliptin 5mg Group: Administration with Evogliptin 5mg and Placebo for 24weeks

        2. Pioglitazone 15mg Group: Administration with Pioglitazone 15mg and Placebo for 24weeks
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
